For debugging:

- Put phone in developer mode:
  Tap 7 times on the Build code in the system settings
  Enable USB debugging
  Enable screen always on when charging

- Launch chrome
  Open developer tools
  Menu -> More tools -> Remote devices

- Connect phone via USB
  Answer prompts

- Get green dot by phone
  Click on device
  Select the tab to examine

To release:
  npm run build

To hot load:
  npm run dev-hot
